DungeonAbomination: The deity and embodiment of the entire Dungeon and its inhabitants. Its destiny is clear: to annihilate the living and to feast off their souls.
StardustAngel: A celestial being made of pure stardust. She is also the guardian of the night sky.
Weaponsmith: A skilled weaponsmith who can transform old weapons into powerful new ones. He is always looking for interesting pieces to work with.